---
const year = new Date().getFullYear();
---

<footer class="bg-surface border-t border-border mt-16">
  <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 py-12">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
      <div>
        <a href="/" class="flex items-center gap-2 text-lg font-bold text-primary">
          <span class="text-xl">∞</span>
          <span>IsItAuDHD</span>
        </a>
        <p class="mt-3 text-text-light text-sm leading-relaxed">
          Free quizzes and resources for understanding the autism + ADHD overlap. Not a diagnostic tool.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h3 class="font-semibold text-text mb-3">Quizzes</h3>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm">
          <li><a href="/quiz/is-it-audhd/" class="text-text-light hover:text-primary transition-colors">Is It AuDHD?</a></li>
          <li><a href="/quiz/autism-or-adhd/" class="text-text-light hover:text-primary transition-colors">Autism or ADHD or Both?</a></li>
          <li><a href="/quiz/audhd-burnout/" class="text-text-light hover:text-primary transition-colors">AuDHD Burnout Check</a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h3 class="font-semibold text-text mb-3">Resources</h3>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm">
